<div class="title">A Good Night's Sleep</div>
<div class="substance">Clonazolam</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Lightsleeper&Exact=1">Lightsleeper</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Lightsleeper. "A Good Night's Sleep: An Experience with Clonazolam (exp105805)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. May 11, 2015. erowid.org/exp/105805</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

